      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;the-emojis-of-kathmandu&#34;&gt;The Emojis of Kathmandu&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;50K tweets between 2012 to 2021 (containing emojis, and geocoded to Kathmandu) show that we really love 😂&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Recently though, we have been 😂   less and 🙏 more, 😁  less and ❤️  more.
Just goes to show Kathmandu is healing from Covid.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ayushsubedi/emojan/main/assets/final.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
